{"id":1644,"date":"2022-09-11T11:14:52","date_gmt":"2022-09-11T11:14:52","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/?p=1644"},"modified":"2022-09-11T11:14:53","modified_gmt":"2022-09-11T11:14:53","slug":"first-aid-is-the-first-and-immediate-assistance","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/first-aid-is-the-first-and-immediate-assistance\/","title":{"rendered":"First Aid Is The First And Immediate Assistance"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>First aid is the first and immediate assistance given to any person suffering from either a minor or serious illness or injury, with care provided to preserve life, prevent the condition from worsening, or promote recovery. It includes initial intervention in a serious condition prior to professional medical help being available, such as performing cardiopulmonary resuscitation (CPR) while waiting for an ambulance, as well as the complete treatment of minor conditions, such as applying a plaster to a cut. Having the practical skills, knowledge, and confidence to act swiftly in the event of a witnessed cardiac arrest is the best chance of helping someone survive an out-of-hospital cardiac arrest until the emergency services can arrive on the scene.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><br>Our staff is well trained, certified, and always ready to help your loved ones.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" src=\"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/First-Aid-2.jpeg\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-1645\" srcset=\"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/First-Aid-2.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/First-Aid-2-300x225.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/First-Aid-2-768x576.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/First-Aid-2-195x146.jpeg 195w, https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/First-Aid-2-50x38.jpeg 50w, https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/First-Aid-2-100x75.jpeg 100w, https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/First-Aid-2-960x720.jpeg 960w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>First aid is the first and immediate assistance given to any person suffering from either a minor or serious illness or injury, with care provided to<span class=\"excerpt-hellip\"> [\u2026]<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":2,"featured_media":1646,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"om_disable_all_campaigns":false,"_mi_skip_tracking":false},"categories":[1],"tags":[9,10,7,8,6],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1644"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/2"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1644"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1644\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":1647,"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1644\/revisions\/1647"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1646"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1644"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1644"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/onpsilverhomes.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=1644"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}